<h1>You've Been Invited to {{organizationName}}</h1>

<p>Hello{{#if firstName}} {{firstName}}{{/if}},</p>

<p>{{invitedByName}} has invited you to join <strong>{{organizationName}}</strong> on the Lifestream Dynamics Accounting Platform.</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Invitation Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
    <p><strong>Role:</strong> {{capitalize role}}</p>
    <p><strong>Invited By:</strong> {{invitedByName}}</p>
    <p><strong>Organization:</strong> {{organizationName}}</p>
</div>

<h2>What's Next?</h2>

<ol>
    <li>Click the button below to accept the invitation</li>
    <li>Create your password to secure your account</li>
    <li>Start collaborating with your team</li>
</ol>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{acceptUrl}}" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
</div>

<p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;">
    {{acceptUrl}}
</p>

<div style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #92400e;">Security Notice</h3>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>This invitation will expire in 7 days</li>
        <li>This link can only be used once</li>
        <li>If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email</li>
        <li>Never share this link with anyone else</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<h2>About Your Role</h2>

{{#if_eq role 'ADMIN'}}
<p>As an <strong>Administrator</strong>, you'll have full access to manage the organization, including:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Managing users and permissions</li>
    <li>Configuring organization settings</li>
    <li>Accessing all financial data</li>
    <li>Managing invoices, quotes, and payments</li>
</ul>
{{else if_eq role 'ACCOUNTANT'}}
<p>As an <strong>Accountant</strong>, you'll have access to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>View and manage all financial records</li>
    <li>Create and edit invoices and quotes</li>
    <li>Process payments and reconciliations</li>
    <li>Generate financial reports</li>
</ul>
{{else if_eq role 'SALES'}}
<p>As a <strong>Sales</strong> team member, you'll be able to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Create and manage quotes</li>
    <li>Track customer interactions</li>
    <li>View sales reports</li>
    <li>Manage customer appointments</li>
</ul>
{{else}}
<p>As a team member, you'll have access to the features assigned to your role.</p>
{{/if_eq}}

<div class="divider"></div>

<p>Welcome to the team!</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The {{organizationName}} Team</p>
